  <div class="row">
    <p class="new-about-title col-12">
      Living Earth is a suite of tools that allow for global consistent classification of land covers and change
      primarily by combining and analysing environmental descriptors with predefined units or categories retrieved or
      classified respectively from Earth observation data.
    </p>
  </div>
  <div class="row">
    <p class="new-about-title col-12">
      Living Earth has been developed through a series of projects that have had an international focus but have
      explored opportunities at a country level.
    </p>
  </div>
